y College, Dublin, Ireland":"диосес оф дублинь, Ирландия","County Kildare, Ireland":"коунти каилдар, Ирландия","lifeSummary":"John Fitzmaurice Fitzgerald 6th Earl of Kildare родился в 1385 г. в местности кастлетоун, коунти каилдар, Ирландия. Его отца звали Gerald FitzMaurice FitzGerald 5th Earl of Kildare. У него был по крайней мере 1 сын от Margaret de la Herne. Он умер 17 октября 1427 г. в местности коунти каилдар, Ирландия в возрасте 42 лет и был похоронен в местности диосес оф дублинь, Ирландия."},"sm":{"1385–17 October 1427":"1385–17 Oketopa 1427","1385–1427":"1385–1427","1395–1432":"1395–1432","1398–1452":"1398–1452","1386–1439":"1386–1439","1421–1477":"1421–1477","1363–1428":"1363–1428","1385":"1385","1363":"1363","1395":"1395","17 October 1427":"17 Oketopa 1427","1477":"1477","1410":"1410","1421":"1421","1432":"1432","1398":"1398","1386":"1386","1452":"1452","1428":"1428","1439":"1439","1427":"1427","Maynooth, Kildare, Ireland":"Maynooth, County Kildare, Aialani","Castletown, County Kildare, Ireland":"Castletown, County Kildare, Aialani","All Hallows, Trinity College, Dublin, Ireland":"Diocese of Dublin, Aialani","County Kildare, Ireland":"County Kildare, Aialani"},"sk":{"1385–17 October 1427":"1385–17. október 1427","1385–1427":"1385–1427","1395–1432":"1395–1432","1398–1452":"1398–1452","1386–1439":"1386–1439","1421–1477":"1421–1477","1363–1428":"1363–1428","1385":"1385","1363":"1363","1395":"1395","17 October 1427":"17. október 1427","1477":"1477","1410":"1410","1421":"1421","1432":"1432","1398":"1398","1386":"1386","1452":"1452","1428":"1428","1439":"1439","1427":"1427","Maynooth, Kildare, Ireland":"Maynooth, County Kildare, Írsko","Castletown, County Kildare, Ireland":"Castletown, County Kildare, Írsko","All Hallows, Trinity College, Dublin, Ireland":"Diocese of Dublin, Írsko","County Kildare, Ireland":"County Kildare, Írsko"},"es":{"1385–17 October 1427":"1385–17 de octubre de 1427","1385–1427":"1385–1427","1395–1432":"1395–1432","1398–1452":"1398–1452"